  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Be the villain! This game will tickle that <u>action-magic-fantasy-nerve</u>, and if you are looking for hours of entertainment: <u>give this game a try</u>! </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>A fast-paced, yet tactical, action-roguelite!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/297d0528f3691a334879e71feeeb93df.poster.avif?t=1756965830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/297d0528f3691a334879e71feeeb93df.webm?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/297d0528f3691a334879e71feeeb93df.mp4?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Storm castles with hordes of undead!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/1bc124adc9964c9cfb329ad99a14deaa.poster.avif?t=1756965830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/1bc124adc9964c9cfb329ad99a14deaa.webm?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/1bc124adc9964c9cfb329ad99a14deaa.mp4?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>...or turn the Empire against itself!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/846796efc1ad92985170c002e01c766c.poster.avif?t=1756965830\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/846796efc1ad92985170c002e01c766c.webm?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/846796efc1ad92985170c002e01c766c.mp4?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>...or just smash it all with brute force!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/038e7df85676eefe0b0cce8e21d26cf1.poster.avif?t=1756965830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/038e7df85676eefe0b0cce8e21d26cf1.webm?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/038e7df85676eefe0b0cce8e21d26cf1.mp4?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Customize your playstyle:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/7d337f31bbc4171c65c287228bd2aab5.poster.avif?t=1756965830\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/7d337f31bbc4171c65c287228bd2aab5.webm?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/7d337f31bbc4171c65c287228bd2aab5.mp4?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Detailed features:</strong></u> (so far, as more will be added)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 playable characters</strong>, each very different from the next. Each has six unique spells, six unique passive skills, and there are 12 base skills anyone can choose from.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrain matters</strong>: Fires spread rapidly on grass, water can be frozen, pits can be fallen into.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wild skill combinations</strong>, allowing for completely unique playthroughs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique items with randomized qualities</strong>, exponentially adding combos and variety to the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>70 Steam Achievements</strong>, which offers varied meta-progression!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each playthrough is a mini-campaign</strong>, starting at a small village and ending in the halls of the emperor's castle. The path will vary, taking you through magical glades, towns, fortresses, or dwarven mines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New game mode</strong>: Last Stand - Survive as long as you can during relentless attacks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>11 unique bosses!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dozens of enemies</strong>, each with variable stats, traits and skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-pixeled coziness</strong>, details, and indie warmth!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique and adventurous <strong>original soundtrack.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hours of fun at a cheap price!</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Be the villain! This game will tickle that <u>action-magic-fantasy-nerve</u>, and if you are looking for hours of entertainment: <u>give this game a try</u>! </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>A fast-paced, yet tactical, action-roguelite!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/297d0528f3691a334879e71feeeb93df.poster.avif?t=1756965830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/297d0528f3691a334879e71feeeb93df.webm?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/297d0528f3691a334879e71feeeb93df.mp4?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Storm castles with hordes of undead!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/1bc124adc9964c9cfb329ad99a14deaa.poster.avif?t=1756965830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/1bc124adc9964c9cfb329ad99a14deaa.webm?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/1bc124adc9964c9cfb329ad99a14deaa.mp4?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>...or turn the Empire against itself!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinli