bc4171c65c287228bd2aab5.mp4?t=1756965830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Detailed features:</strong></u> (so far, as more will be added)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 playable characters</strong>, each very different from the next. Each has six unique spells, six unique passive skills, and there are 12 base skills anyone can choose from.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrain matters</strong>: Fires spread rapidly on grass, water can be frozen, pits can be fallen into.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wild skill combinations</strong>, allowing for completely unique playthroughs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique items with randomized qualities</strong>, exponentially adding combos and variety to the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>70 Steam Achievements</strong>, which offers varied meta-progression!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each playthrough is a mini-campaign</strong>, starting at a small village and ending in the halls of the emperor's castle. The path will vary, taking you through magical glades, towns, fortresses, or dwarven mines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New game mode</strong>: Last Stand - Survive as long as you can during relentless attacks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>11 unique bosses!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dozens of enemies</strong>, each with variable stats, traits and skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-pixeled coziness</strong>, details, and indie warmth!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique and adventurous <strong>original soundtrack.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hours of fun at a cheap price!</strong></p></li></ul>",
